room_title: Escape room "Ship Outta Luck" by Surelocked In in Frederick
room_description:
Hole-y ship - you stole the King's Treasure, and now the Royal Navy is blowing your boat to bits!
The crazy Captain says the rest of the crew can hold them off for an hour while you scamper below deck to find the gold. So shiver some timbers and set some sails, or it's Davy Jones Locker for all ye!
